d=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kor1665702728089.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kor1665702728089.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kor1665702728089.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kor1665702728089\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      checking\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify when constraint checking should be performed.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kor1665702728089__topic_d49892e1_d49893e1_d49894e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kor1665702728089__p_d49895e1_d49896e1_d49897e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">checking</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">deferred</code>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kor1665702728089__section_qbv_grk_3cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d935752e66\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kor1665702728089__p_d49901e1_d49902e1_d49903e1\">Only effective with transaction logging.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kor1665702728089__section_ys1_3rk_3cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d935752e75\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kor1665702728089__p_d49907e1_d49908e1_d49909e1\">This option allows you to determine when constraint\n            checking should be performed—at the end of the statement (‘immediate’) or at the end of\n            the transaction (<code class=\"ph codeph\">deferred</code>).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kor1665702728089__p_d49910e1_d49911e1_d49912e1\">If this option is not present, checking mode is\n            ‘immediate’, meaning that the constraint checking will be performed at the end of the\n            statement.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529308\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529308\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "checking Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 checking Specify when constraint checking should be performed. USYS$INF_PARAMS checking { deferred } Use Only effective with transaction logging. Description This option allows you to determine when constraint checking should be performed—at the end of the statement (‘immediate’) or at the end of the transaction ( deferred ). If this option is not present, checking mode is ‘immediate’, meaning that the constraint checking will be performed at the end of the statement. Was